nodes.text: Kwenn was the Kwenn system's primary planet, orbited by Kwenn Space Station. Kwenn was located on the Ootmian Pabol, and on the dividing line between the Mid Rim and Hutt Space.
Kwenn was the homeworld of Arndall Lott. It was part of the Galactic Empire and later the New Republic.
Kwenn was attacked by the Yuuzhan Vong during their invasion of the galaxy.
